                <h3>📌 Quick Reminder:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Infinitive</strong> = to + base verb (to study, to learn, to teach)</li>
                    <li><strong>Used after:</strong> want, need, decide, hope, plan, try, learn, begin, continue, etc.</li>
                    <li><strong>Example:</strong> "Students need <strong>TO STUDY</strong> hard for exams."</li>
                </ul>
